{"tid":1931853,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"駐港鬼佬開始報復香港人迫佢地戴口罩了","createTime":"2020-03-18T11:18:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T11:47:04.000Z","uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ae3324a6e550b45d21bf429f6d96bf6b92e77c57","tid":1931853,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:18:09.000Z","msg":"港鐵扶手上搽口水 無品外籍男播毒<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情持續，出街最怕遇到人不講衛生、污糟邋遢。有網民影到一個外國男子搭地鐵，刻意拉下口罩，用手指把口水搽在扶手上，行徑令人側目。<br />\n<br />\n「傑出男公關」Facebook專頁分享一段影片，「請廣傳搭地鐵小心！無品鬼佬特登除罩將口水擦落扶手柱」，片中一個外國男士站在車門扶手旁，搭到銅鑼灣站，趁人不注意拉下口罩，手指沾口水搽上扶手，再戴回口罩，其怪異的播毒行為令人摸不著頭腦。<br />\n<br />\n網民大感驚訝，「我唔明做呢啲嘢意義何在」、「佢隊手指入口個下好大機會已中招」，亦有人質問拍攝者「做咩唔出聲？」應該即時制止。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ohpama.com/519092/24parent/%e5%a4%96%e5%9c%8b%e4%ba%ba%e6%90%ad%e6%b8%af%e9%90%b5%e7%a5%9e%e6%83%85%e9%ac%bc%e7%a5%9f%e3%80%80%e6%8b%89%e4%bd%8e/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohpama.com%2F519092%2F24parent%2F%25e5%25a4%2596%25e5%259c%258b%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%2590%25ad%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2590%25b5%25e7%25a5%259e%25e6%2583%2585%25e9%25ac%25bc%25e7%25a5%259f%25e3%2580%2580%25e6%258b%2589%25e4%25bd%258e%2F&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF5Khd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=f443d63c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ohpama.com/519092/24parent/%e5%a4%96%e5%9c%8b%e4%ba%ba%e6%90%ad%e6%b8%af%e9%90%b5%e7%a5%9e%e6%83%85%e9%ac%bc%e7%a5%9f%e3%80%80%e6%8b%89%e4%bd%8e/</a>"},{"pid":"d14027dd619e3109085d6b6201812fb65e620d3b","tid":1931853,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:19:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b7e12144855e26f77386b386278767f800aa5f","tid":1931853,"uid":312242,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:23:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ww2today.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Leonard_Siffleet.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww2today.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F